<plot>Gerald and Josephine used to be in love. Now all that remains of their marriage is an accustomed routine - she brings home money, he struggles at life. One day, as he fantasizes about a beautiful girl who walks past his window, the girl shows up at his door. To make matters worse, his wife returns and discovers them together. As fantasy threatens reality, Gerald must come to terms with his existence and decide what is most important in his life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?652685</url></doc>
